T*
(- GPU Build Notes) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(GPU build behavior is backend-aware:) Tj
T*
(- OpenCL build is attempted broadly,) Tj
T*
(- CUDA build runs only where toolchain and platform support are present,) Tj
T*
(- on macOS, CUDA output may be intentionally absent.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Treat missing CUDA binary on unsupported hosts as expected, not a build failure.) Tj
T*
(- Release Packaging) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Release helper:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This produces timestamped bundles under:) Tj
T*
(- releases/binaries/<timestamp>/) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Recommended release flow:) Tj
T*
(- build all required binaries,) Tj
T*
(- verify pin metadata updates,) Tj
T*
(- run runtime smoke tests in strict mode,) Tj
T*
(- package release payload,) Tj
T*
(- generate and sign checksums for distribution.) Tj
T*
(- Common Failure Modes) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Most frequent issues:) Tj
T*
(- wrong platform artifact loaded,) Tj
T*
(- missing LMDB headers during native build,) Tj
T*
(- hash mismatch after rebuild without metadata update,) Tj
T*
(- strict mode enabled while a required binary is absent.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(First response:) Tj
T*
(- confirm active platform-tag path,) Tj
T*
(- inspect pin metadata for expected digest,) Tj
T*
